<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 12:13:23 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>西岸汽车炸弹：以色列国防军称爆炸物来自同一希伯伦实验室，六名嫌疑人被捕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-car-bombs-idf-says-explosives-came-from-same-hebron-lab/00000191-a7d8-dd1e-adb5-afde7d110000</link><description>以色列国防军封锁了希伯伦，并对嫌疑人展开搜捕。当局认为恐怖组织打算发动更多袭击，并将这些事件与该地区之前发生的汽车爆炸事件联系起来</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 10:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-car-bombs-idf-says-explosives-came-from-same-hebron-lab/00000191-a7d8-dd1e-adb5-afde7d110000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的谎言被揭穿：以色列如何忽视 10 月 7 日灾难的路线图</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-lies-laid-bare-how-israel-ignored-the-roadmap-to-the-october-7-disaster/00000191-9fbc-d453-ab9f-ffbc6ec50000</link><description>反对党领袖亚尔·拉皮德 (Yair Lapid) 在平民调查小组中的证词描绘了一幅可怕的画面 ■ 总理再次修改了自己的简历，但无意中认罪 ■ 没有人知道他是否支持米里·雷格夫 (Miri Regev) 10 月 7 日纪念仪式的计划 ■ 什么不支持亚伊尔·戈兰明白吗？</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 08:00:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-lies-laid-bare-how-israel-ignored-the-roadmap-to-the-october-7-disaster/00000191-9fbc-d453-ab9f-ffbc6ec50000</guid></item><item><title>约旦河西岸发生的两起汽车炸弹袭击事件造成三名以色列人受伤；袭击者被击毙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/two-separate-attacks-in-west-bank-wound-three-israelis-idf-both-used-car-bombs/00000191-a665-dd1e-adb5-aeef8af90000</link><description>两名袭击者几乎同时在西岸附近发动袭击。两名袭击者被杀，三名以色列人受伤。官员估计袭击是经过协调的</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 04:42:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article/.premium/two-separate-attacks-in-west-bank-wound-three-israelis-idf-both-used-car-bombs/00000191-a665-dd1e-adb5-aeef8af90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，两名哈马斯特工在杰宁被杀；操作正在进行中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article-live/three-israelis-wounded-in-separate-attacks-in-west-bank-idf-kills-attackers/00000191-a5f1-d453-ab9f-fdfd81180000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，空军袭击了黎巴嫩南部的真主党目标 ■ 以色列北部加利利西部和北加利利地区火箭警报响起 ■ 内阁批准以色列继续沿费城路线部署，作为可能达成人质交易的条件 ■ 以色列国防军表示，在以色列北部的行动中，已造成 20 人死亡，17 人被拘留约旦河西岸</description><pubDate>Sat, 31 Aug 2024 01:12:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-31/ty-article-live/three-israelis-wounded-in-separate-attacks-in-west-bank-idf-kills-attackers/00000191-a5f1-d453-ab9f-fdfd81180000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 329 天：据报道 Gallant 称，选择要么是人质，要么是费城</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-329-choice-is-either-hostages-or-philadelphi-gallant-reportedly-says/00000191-a418-d172-abd9-ee9ffab20000</link><description>以色列与哈马斯停火协议谈判小组在卡塔尔峰会后返回以色列，消息人士称谈判没有取得突破 ■ 以色列内阁投票决定维持以色列国防军在有争议的费城走廊的存在，只有国防部长加兰特投反对票 ■ 以色列国防军表示它结束了在汗尤尼斯和代尔巴拉赫为期一个月的行动 ■ 这是战争开始 329 天后您需要了解的信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 16:28:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-329-choice-is-either-hostages-or-philadelphi-gallant-reportedly-says/00000191-a418-d172-abd9-ee9ffab20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列游泳运动员阿米·达达翁 (Ami Dadaon) 在 2024 年巴黎残奥会上夺得男子 100 米自由泳金牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-swimmer-ami-dadaon-wins-gold-medal-in-100m-freestyle-in-paris-2024-paralympics/00000191-a3ff-d2ec-a1f7-e7ff94710000</link><description>这位23岁的S4残疾人组100米自由泳世界冠军在残奥会上赢得了职业生涯的第四枚奖牌，也是以色列在巴黎获得的第二枚奖牌，此前阿萨夫·亚苏尔周四在跆拳道比赛中获得金牌</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 16:11:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-swimmer-ami-dadaon-wins-gold-medal-in-100m-freestyle-in-paris-2024-paralympics/00000191-a3ff-d2ec-a1f7-e7ff94710000</guid></item><item><title>一个流氓总理正在把以色列变成一个流氓国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/a-rogue-prime-minister-is-turning-israel-into-a-rogue-state/00000191-a382-d4e9-a199-a7e753cd0000</link><description>如果是为了实现合理的目标，流氓行为并不一定是消极的，但内塔尼亚胡的情况并非如此，他的流氓行为纯粹是指独裁、不诚实，而且常常是邪恶的。只要问问在加沙被扣押的以色列人质的家人就知道了</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 15:49:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/a-rogue-prime-minister-is-turning-israel-into-a-rogue-state/00000191-a382-d4e9-a199-a7e753cd0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡坚持以色列控制费城航线危及人质协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-insistence-on-israeli-control-of-philadelphi-route-jeopardizes-hostage-deal/00000191-a315-d453-ab9f-fb9df7f40000</link><description>鉴于内塔尼亚胡要求以色列在加沙-埃及边境驻军作为停火协议的一部分，调解人正在寻找替代方案，以便为不同的长期安排提供空间。国防部长加兰特严厉批评内塔尼亚胡，称他的决定可能“杀死所有人质”</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 14:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-insistence-on-israeli-control-of-philadelphi-route-jeopardizes-hostage-deal/00000191-a315-d453-ab9f-fb9df7f40000</guid></item><item><title>报道：辛贝特酋长在 10 月 7 日之前警告内塔尼亚胡战争即将来临；总理：没有提到加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/report-shin-bet-chief-warned-netanyahu-of-imminent-war-pm-gaza-not-mentioned/00000191-a2a6-d0ae-af93-e6ff12900000</link><description>据《新消息报》报道，辛贝特安全部门领导人罗南·巴尔 (Ronen Bar) 于 2023 年 7 月警告总理内塔尼亚胡，战争迫在眉睫。反对党领袖 Yair Lapid 向民事调查委员会讲述了 10 月 7 日与辛贝特酋长的会面情况</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 11:34:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/report-shin-bet-chief-warned-netanyahu-of-imminent-war-pm-gaza-not-mentioned/00000191-a2a6-d0ae-af93-e6ff12900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列向最高法院提出：以色列国防军将略微改善斯德泰曼拘留中心的条件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-top-court-idf-will-slightly-improve-conditions-at-sde-teiman-detention-center/00000191-a286-d794-a7f5-f6ffe1f40000</link><description>针对针对臭名昭著的监狱设施运营的请愿书，该州声称将在下个月开放一个新侧翼，这样囚犯就无需全天候戴上手铐，并将新条件与奥弗监狱的条件进行了比较</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 11:13:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-top-court-idf-will-slightly-improve-conditions-at-sde-teiman-detention-center/00000191-a286-d794-a7f5-f6ffe1f40000</guid></item><item><title>为了呼吸一点空气，巴勒斯坦议员躺在牢房门缝下的地板上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-a-bit-of-air-the-palestinian-lawmaker-lies-down-by-the-crack-under-the-cell-door/00000191-9e54-d453-ab9f-fedc4e610000</link><description>巴勒斯坦议员卡利达·贾拉尔在战争爆发后再次被捕，此后一直在没有受到指控的情况下入狱——现在处于完全孤立的状态，处于不人道的条件下</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 11:07:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-08-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/for-a-bit-of-air-the-palestinian-lawmaker-lies-down-by-the-crack-under-the-cell-door/00000191-9e54-d453-ab9f-fedc4e610000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗的“火环”被迫应对利益冲突</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/irans-ring-of-fire-forced-to-navigate-conflicting-interests/00000191-a220-d0ae-af93-e6fdf0d70000</link><description>组成“统一战线”的民兵是有着独立目标的不同团体，其中一些民兵明确表示，他们并不是自动服从德黑兰，他们甚至可能开展与伊朗利益相冲突的行动。例如，胡塞武装可能是伊朗控制最复杂的代理人</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 10:10:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/irans-ring-of-fire-forced-to-navigate-conflicting-interests/00000191-a220-d0ae-af93-e6fdf0d70000</guid></item><item><title>资料来源：以色列内阁批准以色列国防军继续在费城航线上驻扎；勇敢地投反对票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/sources-israeli-cabinet-approves-continued-idf-presence-along-egypt-gaza-border/00000191-a1d4-d453-ab9f-f9dcd1a10000</link><description>国防部长是唯一投票反对这一决定的内阁成员，国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔投了弃权票</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 06:24:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/sources-israeli-cabinet-approves-continued-idf-presence-along-egypt-gaza-border/00000191-a1d4-d453-ab9f-f9dcd1a10000</guid></item><item><title>人质谈判的假面已经破旧，以色列和哈马斯都不愿让步</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/the-hostage-talks-facade-is-wearing-out-and-neither-israel-or-hamas-want-to-budge/00000191-9f49-d172-abd9-ffdf9e840000</link><description>上周发生的所有严峻而动荡的事件并没有改变任何事情：停火谈判毫无进展，因为此时达成的协议对内塔尼亚胡或辛瓦尔没有好处。仪式失败继续发生</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 03:00:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/the-hostage-talks-facade-is-wearing-out-and-neither-israel-or-hamas-want-to-budge/00000191-9f49-d172-abd9-ffdf9e840000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人在约旦河西岸的多次袭击中受伤；以色列国防军称汽车在古什埃齐翁路口发生爆炸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article-live/source-israeli-cabinet-okays-continued-idf-presence-along-contentious-gaza-border-route/00000191-a11f-df21-a9b9-b31fe2310000</link><description>以色列国防军称空军袭击了黎巴嫩南部的真主党目标 ■ 以色列国防军称击毙了哈马斯在杰宁的行动负责人和西岸的另外两名恐怖分子 ■ 内阁批准以色列继续沿费城路线驻扎，作为可能达成人质交易的条件 ■ 世界卫生组织高级官员称以色列军方同意在加沙暂停人道主义行动以开展脊髓灰质炎疫苗接种活动</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 02:49:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article-live/source-israeli-cabinet-okays-continued-idf-presence-along-contentious-gaza-border-route/00000191-a11f-df21-a9b9-b31fe2310000</guid></item><item><title>卡马拉·哈里斯：我不会改变拜登的以色列政策，我们必须完成停火协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/harris-tells-cnn-no-change-in-bidens-israel-policy-we-have-to-get-cease-fire-deal-done/00000191-a0fd-d172-abd9-eaff68f80001</link><description>在作为 2024 年民主党总统候选人首次接受采访时，副总统告诉 CNN，她相信“以色列有权保卫自己”，但补充说“如何做到这一点很重要”</description><pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 02:04:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/harris-tells-cnn-no-change-in-bidens-israel-policy-we-have-to-get-cease-fire-deal-done/00000191-a0fd-d172-abd9-eaff68f80001</guid></item><item><title>以色列最后的、脆弱的反腐败堡垒即将倒塌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/final-bulwark-against-corruption-is-about-to-fall/00000191-9fbb-d0ae-af93-ffffb7b30000</link><description>过去几年对反腐败战争不利，让本·格维尔任命下一任警察调查部门负责人将对其造成致命打击。然后是内塔尼亚胡，他寻求完全接管公务员制度</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 22:45:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/final-bulwark-against-corruption-is-about-to-fall/00000191-9fbb-d0ae-af93-ffffb7b30000</guid></item><item><title>特朗普最高外交政策顾问警告：如果英国停止向以色列出售武器，特殊关系将面临风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/trumps-foreign-policy-aide-special-relationship-at-risk-if-uk-halts-arms-sales-to-israel/00000191-a02d-d453-ab9f-f8ad6aa20000</link><description>罗伯特·奥布莱恩（Robert O&amp;#39;Brien）在接受伦敦政策交流智囊团采访时表示，如果特朗普11月获胜，他可能会进入特朗普内阁，英国的武器禁运“将真正伤害西方联盟和北约”</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 22:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/trumps-foreign-policy-aide-special-relationship-at-risk-if-uk-halts-arms-sales-to-israel/00000191-a02d-d453-ab9f-f8ad6aa20000</guid></item><item><title>资料来源：以色列司法部长威胁要改变主要司法委员会的组成</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/sources-israeli-justice-minister-threatens-to-change-makeup-of-key-judicial-committee/00000191-9fbd-d172-abd9-ffbf26e90000</link><description>据报道，亚里夫·莱文告诉代理首席大法官，如果他的最高法院候选人未获批准，他和其他部长也将加紧努力罢免以色列总检察长</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 21:14:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-30/ty-article/.premium/sources-israeli-justice-minister-threatens-to-change-makeup-of-key-judicial-committee/00000191-9fbd-d172-abd9-ffbf26e90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列跆拳道运动员阿萨夫·亚苏尔 (Asaf Yasur) 在 2024 年巴黎残奥会上获得金牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-taekwondo-athlete-asaf-yasur-takes-gold-medal-in-paris-2024-paralympics/00000191-9fa3-d0ae-af93-ffff75260000</link><description>22岁的亚苏尔在男子残疾人跆拳道比赛中排名世界第一，并且是两届世界冠军。他在男子-58公斤级比赛中击败了世界排名第二的土耳其选手阿里·坎·奥兹坎，为以色列赢得了第385枚残奥会奖牌。</description><pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 20:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-29/ty-article/.premium/israels-taekwondo-athlete-asaf-yasur-takes-gold-medal-in-paris-2024-paralympics/00000191-9fa3-d0ae-af93-ffff75260000</guid></item></channel></rss>